Package: copilot.sdk.supercharged
Title: R SDK for GitHub Copilot CLI
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Microsoft Corporation", role = c("aut", "cph")),
    person("GitHub", role = "aut")
  )
Description: R SDK for programmatic control of GitHub Copilot CLI via JSON-RPC 2.0
    over stdio. Provides session management, tool registration, event handling,
    and streaming support for building applications on top of GitHub Copilot.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/jeremiahjordanisaacson/copilot-sdk-supercharged
